# Public Repository

This repo is PUBLIC. NEVER add secrets, tokens, credentials, personal data, private keys, or internal hostnames. Use runtime env vars for secrets.

# Maintain Docs

When you change the repo, update `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, and any affected `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md` or `.cursor/rules/` to stay in sync. `README.md` is the user-facing doc — if behavior, commands, or conventions change, it must be updated too. Outdated docs are worse than none.
